---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Feature Flags Without the $50K Bill">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block rounded-full bg-indigo-50 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-700 mb-6 ring-1 ring-indigo-100">
      OpenFeature-native from day one
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-6xl">
      Feature flags<br/>
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">without the $50K bill</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
      FeatureSignals is a developer-first feature management platform with transparent pricing,
      sub-10ms evaluation, and genuine multi-deployment flexibility.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#" class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:shadow-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2">Start Free</a>
      <a href="#" class="rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-400 focus:ring-offset-2">View Docs</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-xl rounded-xl bg-slate-950 p-6 text-left ring-1 ring-white/10 shadow-2xl">
      <div class="flex gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-400/80"></span>
        <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400/80"></span>
        <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-400/80"></span>
      </div>
      <pre class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300"><code><span class="text-indigo-400">import</span> featuresignals <span class="text-indigo-400">from</span> <span class="text-emerald-400">'@featuresignals/node'</span>;

<span class="text-indigo-400">const</span> client = featuresignals.init(<span class="text-emerald-400">'sdk-key-xxx'</span>);

<span class="text-indigo-400">if</span> (client.boolVariation(<span class="text-emerald-400">'new-checkout'</span>, user, <span class="text-amber-400">false</span>)) &#123;
  showNewCheckout();
&#125;</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-20 border-y border-slate-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Why FeatureSignals?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-slate-500">Everything your engineering team needs, nothing it doesn't.</p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">Transparent Pricing</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Flat tier pricing. No per-MAU charges. Unlimited flags and evaluations on every plan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">Sub-10ms Evaluation</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">SDKs evaluate locally with zero network calls. Rules sync via streaming.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 119 0v3.75M3.75 21.75h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">Zero Lock-in</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">OpenFeature-native SDKs. Switch providers without rewriting code.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">Deploy Anywhere</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">SaaS, private cloud, or on-premises. Single Go binary. Air-gap capable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">Stale Flag Detection</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Mandatory expiration dates, code scanning, and automated cleanup.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">Enterprise Ready</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">SSO, RBAC, audit logs, approval workflows. SOC 2 compliant.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Simple, transparent pricing</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-500">No per-MAU charges. Unlimited flags on every plan.</p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-8 text-left transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Free</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">$0<span class="text-base font-normal text-slate-500">/mo</span></p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>1 project, 2 environments</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Unlimited flags & evaluations</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Up to 3 team members</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg border border-slate-300 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-400 focus:ring-offset-2">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-indigo-600 p-8 text-left relative shadow-lg shadow-indigo-100">
          <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white">Popular</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Pro</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">$49<span class="text-base font-normal text-slate-500">/seat/mo</span></p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Unlimited projects & environments</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>SSO (SAML, OIDC)</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Audit log, webhooks</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white transition-all hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:shadow-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2">Start Pro Trial</a>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-8 text-left transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Enterprise</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">$149<span class="text-base font-normal text-slate-500">/seat/mo</span></p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Everything in Pro</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Private cloud / on-premises</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Dedicated support (4h SLA)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg border border-slate-300 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-400 focus:ring-offset-2">Contact Sales</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-indigo-800 py-16 text-center text-white">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Ready to ship faster?</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-indigo-200">Start managing feature flags in under 5 minutes.</p>
    <a href="#" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-600 shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-indigo-700">Get Started Free</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
